Post workout chill with @drinkviveau_sg fresh pressed sparkling water, a healthier alternative to high sugar sodas🥤💦
.
No added sugar and preservatives, Viveau drinks come directly from orchards in Canada. Not only do they taste good, they are all natural and great for post workout hydration. Best to have it chilled - the drink and mood - along with a magazine 😎📖
.
Purchase from @lazada_sg
https://www.lazada.sg/shop/wholesome-food-people
